This is a Semtiment Analysis project which uses the twitter comments and train the BIdirectional LSTM and predict the sentiment of a text as Neutral, Negative or positive.

Steps to run the project:

Step 1 - Run command python main.py  -- This will train the model and will also save it for the use of app.py and predictions. This
                                          step will also save the Tokenizer and Label encoder  used file training.
Step 2 - Run command streamlit run app.py  -- This will use the trained model ins above step to give the predictions
